            <img class="thumbnailIMG" src="/images/DiceGame.png" alt="Dice Roll" />
                <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Dice Game <span id="expandText3">...show more</span> <span id="hiddenText3" hidden > This is a game created with Java Script which randomly generates two numbers from 1 - 6, loads the corresponding dice image 
